main event: Multiple black and white photographs of a UFO sighting in Albuquerque, New Mexico, in 1963.
interesting points: The photographs depict various sightings of disc-shaped or circular objects among the trees,The images are labeled as 'UNCLASSIFIED' and are associated with the Foreign Technology Division, AFSC,Several photographs show an unidentified vehicle obscured by foliage,The quality of the photographs varies, with some being blurry and indistinct,This report is part of Project Blue Book, which investigated UFO sightings.
sighted object: unidentified flying objects (UFOs) or aerial phenomena
